sentences.sentence: Vineyards are located in the cool pre-cordillera areas of Curico Valley and Maule Valley.
sentences.translation: 葡萄园位于克里库山谷和马勒山谷较寒冷的山地。

sentences.sentence: After this trek You are physically fit and very well acclimatised to stick to any summit in the Cordillera Blanca.
